race.description: Supporting The Mcgrath Foundation E&G Handicap (62)
race.comment: AUTUMN FROST (1) was an impressive winner two back at Morphettville Parks when going quick in front. Not as effective last time but is sure to give himself every chance again up on speed. OUTPOST (4) turned things around last start when getting the verdict at headquarters. Tackling a deeper field this time but he is capable of another big run. TRIPOD TERROR (9) doesn't win out of turn and was too bad to be true last start when tailing out. Can bounce back sharply third-up. CORK HARBOUR (2) stuck on gamely into the placings last time. Backs up quickly and is going well without winning. Doesn't need to improve much to go close again. Last start winner BIG MAV (5) will find this tougher but boasts a solid record over this journey and is worth keeping safe.
